sync == untill 1 operation is completed the other operations cannot b executed
async == user can perform multipe operations without blocking the javascript engine

Jvascript is default synchronus but it becomes async in two cases
1 ->  Browser API/Web API events or functions. These include methods like setTimeout,or eventhandlers
2- promises

